T1  - Risk Premium Shocks and the Zero Bound on Nominal Interest Rates
AU  - AMANO, ROBERT
AU  - SHUKAYEV, MALIK
Y1  - 2012/12/01
PY  - 2012
DA  - 2012/12/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1538-4616.2012.00541.x
